RelatedSentence: PRESTON - It was the feel - good moment of the week when about 400 residents joined together in support of Mid-Shore 's smallest citizens - babies - by participating in the 2014 March for Babies to benefit the March of Dimes .

PRESTON - It was the feel - good moment of the week when about 400 residents joined together in support of Mid-Shore 's smallest citizens - babies - by participating in the 2014 March for Babies to benefit the March of Dimes .
On May 4 , the Preston Autoplex was packed with strollers , families and corporate teams who are projected to have raised more than $ 90,000 to help babies be born healthy .
On May 4 , the Preston Autoplex was packed with strollers , families and corporate teams who are projected to have raised more than $ 90,000 to help babies be born healthy .
In total , they walked 1,600 miles .

Special guests included the 2014 March for Babies Chairman Dave Wilson , president / CEO of Preston Automotive Group , and the Morris Family , the 2014 Eastern Shore of Maryland Ambassador Family , who joined walkers on the route .
March for Babies donations fund research , education and community programs to help women have full - term pregnancies and healthy babies .

We were overwhelmed with pride as 90 adults and 51 children joined our family team , Mallory 's Marchers , at the March for Babies walk this past Sunday , said Nikki Morris , whose family served as the 2014 March of Dimes Ambassador Family .
